description: Product Description Prices start at just 69p per mask Eye holes pre-cut Delivery included High quality 350GSM card stock Includes Elastic/Sticks & Fixings Personalised Face Masks Includes everything you'll need Our high quality personalised face masks come with the eye holes pre-cut. Choose from cut at home (DIY), precut or ready to wear masks. Whether you're planning a stag do, hen do, a birthday party, or any kind of event, our face masks will take it to another level. Simply upload your photo and we'll send your masks in the post. Cut at Home, Precut and Ready to Wear Cut at home (DIY) - we will cut out the eyes for you, but you'll need to cut out the masks & attach the fixings at home. We supply everything, all you need is a sharp pair of scissors. Precut - we cut out the eyes & the masks for you, so all you'll need to do at home is apply the supplied fixings. Ready to wear - We do everything for you - the masks will come cut out with the fixings attached. What makes a great mask? High quality images For a high quality image, the bigger the photo the better. The best images to send us are direct from your phone camera or PC. To check if the photo is high quality, try zooming into the picture on your device and see how it looks! Forward facing images A forward facing shot only is heavily advised - looking at the camera please! No closed eyes are best for an ideal finished product. Close-up photo Close-ups are best, if they're in the distance they'll be fuzzy! *Note* Any problems with your photo may delay your order. How to order your masks Click Customise Now to begin the process Add Your Photo & Contact Details. Follow the process through to completion. We print & post your masks We'll process your order and put them in the post within 2 business days. Your masks will arrive in good time, ready for you to cut out and assemble (if ordering cut at home/precut). It doesn't take long and it's really simple to do. We provide everything you need to assemble your masks as easily as possible (elastic/sticks, sticky tabs, printed masks and assembly instructions). You just need some scissors! If you order ready to wear, the masks come fully assembled so no work is required at home. What you need to do at home - Cut at Home & Precut Pop out the eye cut outs (very satisfying). Grab a good pair of scissors and cut around the face shape. This is required for cut at home only, precut masks are cut out by us. Then, just take the sticky tabs and place them over the strings and onto the mask. You're good to go! Enjoy & send us photos! Now that you have your masks ready - you're bound to make the party go with a bang and keep you and your guests laughing for the rest of the night! Have fun, enjoy the masks, and take loads of pictures you can later share with us! Step 1 Step 2 Step 3 Step 4
